text: I was at SL last year for the first time (can't make it this year). If your company or org can sponsor you to go -- or if you want to just shell out the cash to go yourself -- I recommend doing so. It's a really cool conference filled with interesting people. Plus one of the nights they rent out the Saint Louis city museum which is one of the most fun places I've ever been
